      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 77,
      "message": "This piece of code is duplicated on both subclasses. I would add a method to PrepareCdsCallDelegate class like:\n\n    protected AbstractCDSPropertiesBean prepareCDSPropertiesBean(DelegateExecution delegateExecution,\n            PnfResourceCustomization pnfResourceCustomization, String action, String jsonRequest) {\n        AbstractCDSPropertiesBean cdsPropertiesBean = new AbstractCDSPropertiesBean();\n        cdsPropertiesBean.setBlueprintName(pnfResourceCustomization.getBlueprintName());\n        cdsPropertiesBean.setBlueprintVersion(pnfResourceCustomization.getBlueprintVersion());\n        cdsPropertiesBean.setOriginatorId(ORIGINATOR_ID);\n        cdsPropertiesBean.setActionName(action);\n        cdsPropertiesBean.setMode(MODE);\n        cdsPropertiesBean.setRequestId((String) delegateExecution.getVariable(MSO_REQUEST_ID));\n        cdsPropertiesBean.setSubRequestId((String) delegateExecution.getVariable(PNF_UUID));\n        cdsPropertiesBean.setRequestObject(jsonRequest);\n        return cdsPropertiesBean;\n    }\n\nAnd then just invoke the method here:\n\nreturn prepareCDSPropertiesBean(delegateExecution,\n                pnfResourceCustomization, ACTION_NAME, configAssignRequest.toString());",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 2789,
        "name": "Lukasz Muszkieta",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "lukasz.muszkieta@nokia.com",
        "username": "lukaszM"
      },
